@startuml
title Diagrama de secuencia - Registrar inspección y generar informe

actor Inspector
participant "Frontend React" as FE
participant "FastAPI Routes" as API
participant "inspectionservice" as InspectionSvc
participant "inspectionfieldservice" as FieldSvc
participant "evidenceservice" as EvidenceSvc
participant "ocrservice / validationservice" as OCRSvc
participant "transcriptionservice" as TranscriptionSvc
participant "reportdraftservice" as DraftSvc
participant "LangChain + Ollama\nLLaMA 3" as LLM
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
collections "Storage" as FS

== Registro de inspección ==
Inspector -> FE : Completa formulario inicial
FE -> API : POST /inspections
API -> InspectionSvc : createInspection(payload)
InspectionSvc -> DB : INSERT Inspection
DB --> InspectionSvc : inspectionId
InspectionSvc --> API : Inspection creada
API --> FE : 201 Created

== Registro de campos ==
loop Por cada campo estructurado
  FE -> API : POST /inspections/{id}/fields
  API -> FieldSvc : createInspectionField(payload)
  FieldSvc -> DB : INSERT InspectionField
  DB --> FieldSvc : ok
  FieldSvc --> API : campo registrado
  API --> FE : 201 Created
end

== Carga de evidencias ==
loop Por cada evidencia
  FE -> API : POST /inspections/{id}/evidences
  API -> EvidenceSvc : createEvidence(file, metadata)
  EvidenceSvc -> FS : guardar archivo
  EvidenceSvc -> DB : INSERT Evidence
  DB --> EvidenceSvc : evidenceId
  EvidenceSvc --> API : evidencia registrada
  API --> FE : 201 Created
end

== OCR y validación ==
FE -> API : POST /ocr/evidences/{evidenceId}/extract
API -> OCRSvc : extractTextFromEvidence(evidenceId)
OCRSvc -> FS : leer imagen
OCRSvc -> OCRSvc : preprocessImage()
OCRSvc -> OCRSvc : Tesseract OCR
OCRSvc -> DB : UPDATE Evidence.ocr*
DB --> OCRSvc : ok
OCRSvc --> API : texto extraído
API --> FE : OCR result

FE -> API : POST /ocr/inspections/{id}/validate
API -> OCRSvc : validateInspectionOCR(id)
OCRSvc -> DB : SELECT fields + evidences
OCRSvc -> OCRSvc : comparar manualValue vs ocrValue
OCRSvc -> DB : UPDATE InspectionField.validation*
DB --> OCRSvc : resumen de validación
OCRSvc --> API : matched/mismatched/notfound
API --> FE : validation summary

== Transcripción ==
opt Existe audio de observaciones
  FE -> API : POST /transcription
  API -> TranscriptionSvc : createAndProcessTranscription(payload)
  TranscriptionSvc -> FS : leer audio
  TranscriptionSvc -> TranscriptionSvc : Whisper transcribe()
  TranscriptionSvc -> DB : INSERT Transcription
  DB --> TranscriptionSvc : transcriptionId
  TranscriptionSvc --> API : transcripción generada
  API --> FE : transcription result
end

== Generación de borrador ==
Inspector -> FE : Solicita generar informe
FE -> API : POST /report-drafts/generate/{inspectionId}
API -> DraftSvc : generateReportDraft(inspectionId, templateVersion)
DraftSvc -> DB : SELECT inspection + fields + evidences + transcriptions
DB --> DraftSvc : snapshot de datos
DraftSvc -> DraftSvc : renderTemplate() / buildContext()
DraftSvc -> LLM : generar secciones del informe
LLM --> DraftSvc : summary/findings/recommendations/finalReport
DraftSvc -> DB : INSERT ReportDraft
DB --> DraftSvc : draftId
DraftSvc --> API : borrador generado
API --> FE : 201 Created + draft

@enduml